exact_source: Cullen Metals Pty Ltd, “Cullen” or “the Company,” a wholly-owned subsidiary of Cullen Resources Limited, has signed a Binding Term Sheet to acquire up to a 90% interest in Exploration Licence Application E63/2463 (~ 150 sq. km) in the Eastern Goldfields of Western Australia ("Application" or "Tenement") – ASX:CUL; 28-11-2024.
